            <title>联想 YOGA 27 2022 一体机降至 5999 元：R7 6800H + 4K 屏</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/723/940.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/723/940.htm</guid>
